      <title>瑞士通胀意外放缓至 2021 年年中以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/swiss-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-to-weakest-since-mid-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士通胀意外放缓，增强了进一步降息的理由，并加剧了人们对央行通胀目标可能低于预期的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/swiss-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-to-weakest-since-mid-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称伊朗计划通过代理人攻击以色列，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称伊朗可能准备在未来几天从伊拉克领土袭击以色列，油价因此上涨，市场将注意力重新转移到中东地区可能爆发的敌对行动上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 23:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
